description:
Wash the day away with Christophe Robin’s Luscious Curl Cleansing Balm. Formulated for curly to coily hair types, this 2-in-1 formula cleanses, detangles, and nourishes curly to coily hair while helping to define and soften for curls with bounce and shine.&nbsp; 
 Key Ingredients:&nbsp;&nbsp;  

 Kokum Butter: conditions dry hair and scalp&nbsp; 
 Creatine: strengthens hair to prevent breakage and damage&nbsp; 
 Chia Seed Oil: adds softness&nbsp; 
 Flaxseed Milk: helps define curls for touchable hold with bounce and shine&nbsp; 

 Key Benefits: &nbsp; 

 Cleanses, detangles and nourishes curly to coily hair&nbsp; 
 Non-lathering, balmy texture&nbsp; 
 Hydrates and defines curls&nbsp; 
 Creates a frizz-free, shiny finish&nbsp;

Deep clean your scalp and achieve the perfect canvas for gorgeous hair with the Grow Gorgeous Scalp Detox Scrub. Just as flawless make-up starts with primed skin, a scalp exfoliator lays the foundation for flourishing strands. Skincare shouldn’t stop at your hairline, so level up your routine with this essential first step in your haircare routine.&nbsp; 
The purifying pre-wash treatment instantly detoxifies and refreshes scalps with a tendency for grease and product build-up, going the extra mile to help get the very best out of your hair. The powerful scalp-clarifying formula balances excess sebum and gently buffs away follicle-clogging grime caused by urban pollution, plus other dulling impurities that can scupper hair’s potential.&nbsp; 
&nbsp;

Restore hair and scalp with the Black Baccara Haircare Christmas Set from miriam quevedo. This festive hair care set is designed to reverse the signs of aging and transform hair back to a healthier state.&nbsp; It works from the follicle to the fiber to stimulate growth and delivers superior rejuvenation, strength and hydration for healthier, shinier hair with renewed texture and manageability.&nbsp; 
 Black Baccara Haircare Christmas Set 2021 includes:&nbsp;&nbsp;  

 Shampoo (250 ml.): A luxurious and restorative treatment shampoo.&nbsp; 
 Mask (250 ml.): A reparative hair growth mask.&nbsp; 
 Texturizing Wave Mist Spray (150 ml.): A hair texturizing spray to give your hair a shinier look.&nbsp; 

 Key Ingredients:&nbsp;  
 Black Baccara Rose Youth Concentrate:  provides intense protection against internal and external stressors, while constantly adapting based on lifestyle and environment to prevent and defend against aging caused prematurely by our daily routines&nbsp; 
 Fresh Rose Stem Cells:  contains special epigenetic factors and metabolites to preserve hair follicle’s stem cells’ function, increasing stem cell vitality, boosting regeneration and protecting against environmental stress&nbsp; 
 Hair Growth Factors:  act at the heart of hair follicle, targeting multiple hair growth regulators, to prevent and stop hair loss while also stimulating growth&nbsp; 
 Key Benefits:&nbsp;  

 Gently cleanses while preventing hair growth disturbances due to our environment and lifestyle&nbsp; 
 Intensely moisturizes, nourishes and revitalizes hair and scalp while preventing hair growth disturbances due to our environment and lifestyle&nbsp; 
 Adds volume and texture&nbsp;
